# ‚úàÔ∏è Flight Booking Web App

A responsive and dynamic flight booking web application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This project integrates real-time flight search and booking APIs, supports multi-step booking flows, and generates downloadable receipts.

---

## üöÄ Features

- **Modern UI Design**: Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript for a clean, intuitive user experience.
- **Flight Search Integration**: Connects to external APIs to fetch live flight data.
- **Dynamic Pricing**: Displays real-time prices in search results based on API responses.
- **Multi-Step Booking Flow**: Guides users through flight selection, passenger details, payment, and confirmation.
- **PNR Generation**: Displays a unique Passenger Name Record (PNR) after successful booking.
- **Receipt Generation**: Allows users to download booking receipts in PDF or JSON format.
- **Final Polish & Testing**: Includes UI refinements, bug fixes, and performance optimizations.

---

## üõ†Ô∏è Tech Stack

| Layer         | Technology         |
|--------------|--------------------|
| Frontend     | HTML, CSS, JavaScript |
| APIs         | Flight Search & Booking APIs (e.g., Amadeus, Skyscanner, etc.) |
| PDF Export   | jsPDF or html2pdf.js |
| JSON Export  | Native JS Blob & FileSaver.js |
| Deployment   | GitHub Pages / Netlify / Vercel |

